title: Extract Kth Character From The Rope Tree

content.content: Unfortunately, as of this writting, the description omits to say that the len of a node is the sum of the length of the strings in the leafs of the subtree defined by that node, which is a key observation to solve this problem efficiently.
Agreed. You can intuit it, but it took me an embarrassing amount of time to realize it. This problem should be updated
